{"tid":56240,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳蘋果將針對iPhone十週年推出三部新機 代號：法拉利","createTime":"2016-12-27T05:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T02:58:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a43f0034e0f5a4b08fb3d9a28650e1caffc5a5b","tid":56240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"電玩圈熱話－iPhone 10th Anniversary 將推出 3 個型號 <br />\n內部代號為「Ferrari」的 iPhone 8，將有 3 大重大變革，包括訂價！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/hk/2016/12/iphone-8-price-apple\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fhk%2F2016%2F12%2Fiphone-8-price-apple&d=ho%2FvgKfURKTm3ZkMQb2G0UsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=def40568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/hk/2016/12/iphone-8-price-apple</a>"},{"pid":"64bec54579423e24530d8b33e418f6c63e46075b","tid":56240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/hk.hypebeast.com/files/2016/12/iphone-8-price-apple1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2016%2F12%2Fiphone-8-price-apple1.jpg&h=364159eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n科技網證 BGR 轉述微博用戶預測，Apple 將會在 iPhone 10 週年之際，破例一口氣推出 3 款 iPhone，該微博用戶近來幾次預言皆準，故有參考價值。 <br />\n<br />\n3 款手機型號未能確定，暫稱之為 iPhone 7s、iPhone 7s Plus 與 iPhone 8，前兩者將會如 iPhone 6 與 6s 一般，外觀設計沒有重大差別，重點提升機能；至於 iPhone 8 將會有重大改革。Apple 開發團隊稱之為 Ferrari，將有全新外觀設計，其一是以虛擬 Home 鍵取代實際按鍵，並首度起用 AMOLED 屏幕制式。配合全新設計，Apple 將會改動一體電路主板，iPhone 8 主板將會一分為二，一邊裝上 A11 新一代晶片與 NAND 閃存硬件，另一邊則是 wi-fi、天線等接收部件，兩塊主板間有特殊柔軟電線連接。最令人關注的預測，是 Apple 將會首次打破有增無減的新 iPhone 訂價規律，下調 iPhone 7s、iPhone 7s Plus 與 iPhone 8 訂價！如果一切屬實，肯定能吸引更多人轉用 iPhone。"},{"pid":"59a5fa830edfc9c053b6520b12abc78449d30bf6","tid":56240,"uid":4658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/135110_7f0f23c92f8c5d1dd024bc4f908ce62c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F135110_7f0f23c92f8c5d1dd024bc4f908ce62c.jpg&h=48950a9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd05010008308c33dd570792ba13d540dabf74f5","tid":56240,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死"},{"pid":"d503ce14aa877c957f3948f6c889519daebba2de","tid":56240,"uid":33971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"法拉利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會有紅蘋果？"},{"pid":"2c59c1c35585236324b247e912b4e6f8ee86f645","tid":56240,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"價錢只包淨機<br />\n紙盒電線earphone說明書Apple貼紙另計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb220e5df28d3dbe302327a7eb25179d2a187f40","tid":56240,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"貴到買唔起？"},{"pid":"6daf4d7c1d9ccc8d6caa674f803bdba030feb7c4","tid":56240,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>價錢只包淨機<br />\n紙盒電線earphone說明書Apple貼紙另計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪又好呀，其他跟機垃圾仲唔嫌多？"},{"pid":"e1dfa5b7f71f6bb7c6302a6d9bc39590777bf1e1","tid":56240,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>價錢只包淨機<br />\n紙盒電線earphone說明書Apple貼紙另計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im