={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過假相就唔好深究啦 又唔係真機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦 圖就緊係假嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過文入邊講既野 都唔假得去邊<br />\n近幾年 年年都流出<br />\n而流出既野 又係真既"},{"pid":"97a532190d48e02940588b003dda6b90f4633b9c","tid":56240,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有iphone8咁點解會想買iphone7s？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三個月前出咗iPhone 7，都仲有好多人買6S"},{"pid":"0c472d8099a54c04422adbcbd659ea28b13b3dd6","tid":56240,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果有iphone8咁點解會想買iphone7s？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三個月前出咗iPhone 7，都仲有好多人買6S</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次一次過出兩代<br />\n可能7s/plus跟返今年7嘅價<br />\n跟住8再賣貴啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6151001f00cd5442bf6367baed111c54c61e197f","tid":56240,"uid":18633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果有iphone8咁點解會想買iphone7s？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三個月前出咗iPhone 7，都仲有好多人買6S</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次一次過出兩代<br />\n可能7s/plus跟返今年7嘅價<br />\n跟住8再賣貴啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反為想知下年會唔會有64GB嘅7plus"}]}